^B@2^*BAndy Hung: ^*N|cp||at|Bidding:  Your partner has a shown a pretty good hand by Doubling and bidding 3@d. We have most likely a double stopper in spades, the @HA as well as three card diamond support. Therefore you should co-operate with partner by not passing, but by bidding 3NT instead.|
